10 new effects in one update! No jokes ;)
<br>
<br>- go to 'Art Backgrounds' to start your galactic adventure or add some mystery to your photos;
<br>- say 'NO' to boring pictures with three new effects from the 'Face Montages' category;
<br>- be on the bright side with a new 'Drawing vs Photography' template;
<br>- try 'Deyemond' on to make your eyes sparkle. Go to 'Makeover' for the effect;
<br>- once you applied one of the forenamed filters, go to 'Simple Frames' to finish your edit with one of three new frames.

Ready for something new? Then meet our new amazing arrivals! Update your app now and enjoy the variety of awesome filters and stunning effects:
<br>- My Own Self-ish Background (Customizable Effects);
<br>- Yellow Self-ish Background (Smart Filters);
<br>- In One Glow (Art Backgrounds).
<br>By the way, the app should be running a bit faster with the update.

